<h3>Overview</h3>
<b>Welcome to the Human TSP Solver!</b> 
The idea of this project is to:
<b>(1)</b> Partition instances of the TSP into sub-problems, 
<b>(2)</b> Use human spatial intelligence to solve sub-problems, and 
<b>(3)</b> Aggregate contributions into a crowdsourced solution. 
<small>(<%= link_to 'learn more', :controller => 'home', :action => 'about' %>...)</small>

